<br>
If I just want a port I do a /who wiz, or /who druid and give a direct tell and ask them if they have the time would they mind teleporting me to x location for 50pp, and if they are busy just say so no worries.. and if they say no I ALWAYS say Thanks anyway good hunting to you. I used to feel that it was kind of rude to give a direct tell for a port to a druid wizzie, but now I feel if they dont want to be bombarded with tells for ports they will exercise the /role /anon functions in the game.<br>
<br>
My prefered method of getting a teleport if I have time is to simply wait for that druid/wizzie /auctioning porting to any location for donations. When I take a ride from these ppl I quickly sum up there Twink status and make a donation according to what state of riches I feel they have. If its a person well dressed and obviously just trying to make a few extra pp I donate 30 pp, if its a Translocate from that type of person I donate 30pp. if its a lvl 29-40ish druid/wizzie that is obviously hoping to make what ever they can cause they need the cash I generally donate 50-100pp depending on what state of pocket cash I have atm.<br>
<br>
I have a wizard alt. and he has never taken any donations what so ever to port people. And now that Translocate is out I will even answer FAR more of the /ooc /auc I see for people asking for Teleports.<br>
<br>
Clerics on the other hand I feel totally different about. Anyone who has any clue what so ever about what the cost is to simply exist as a post 50 cleric would ALWAYS donate I believe. I have had many clerics say to me dont worry about donating (usually the clicker clerics) and I have always asked them to please look at my donation as a stack of 10 peridots, not as 150 pp. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usandin54.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sandin54</A> at: 12/22/01 11:21:24 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uschande.showPublicProfile?language=EN>schande</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New to the block</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/23/01 12:41:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=221.topic&index=64>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Always pay for TP and ress?</span><hr size=1> imo these pps for a 49 or 56 rez are a laugh compared to the time you'd unrezzed spend to regain same state of exp back when lvl 50+, so i always pay well of course.<br>
