As for rezes... well, i'm a level 60 Cleric (non-epic) who has never been /anon or /roleplay.  If I am able, i will (and have) crossed the entire world to rez someone i dont know for absolutely nothing.  I dont (usually) charge for rezes and I rarely accept donations.  <br>
